content: @@naurking5388 Hotel capacity in Rio is always very high, not necessary this expensive and polemic concert. Brazil is used to do big parties like Reveillon, concerts and the biggest Carnival in the world. This is just a polemic concert that should have been avoided, especially because we are living a tragedu caused by flood inudetion in Brazil South. It is not time for this kind of party, seems like 1 million people are jumping in peoples sadness, tragedy and grief.
